{
  "stem": "11882.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And she called up and said, this is very startling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was in spring 1947.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The Goering trial was all gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And here comes the plan, the master plan-- how it was planned out and how it was distributed so all the agencies would know it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And after they left the meeting, the [NON-ENGLISH], Eichmann and Heydrich-- Heydrich had to go off to Prague.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was in charge of Prague at that moment before he, himself, was murdered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And after the meeting, they had a little whiskey by the fireside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It's a beautiful villa in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "If you go to Berlin, you should visit it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he said, well, now we have-- even-- even the popes of the-- of the civil service are backing us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Because there was almost no protest in this meeting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But there were a few protests.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And funny reasons-- that might have been to kind of call the crazy dogs off, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One man said, well, wouldn't it be better to wait until the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had different-- three or four of them did make a very mild effort to protest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after the war when Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Kempner was interrogating these people in Nuremberg, he asked all these people if they'd been at that meeting.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, no, I never had anything to do with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, well, what about this?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, I don't know why you don't say you were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You were one of the very few who spoke up against it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they didn't want to have anything to do with it, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they didn't know it was so beautifully documented.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, of course, Eichmann and Heydrich had a very good reason for documenting it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't do it-- this whole group of the government did it.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
